CURRENT VERSION
    1.0.4

WHEN RELEASING A NEW VERSION
    1.: update whatever needed
    2.: update "version" key in package.json
    3.: run "grunt build" and "grunt"
    4.: commit and add new version tag (GitHub tag) (do NOT push immediately)
    5.: push all to GitHub
    6.: run "npm publish"
    7.: update CURRENT VERSION here

FUTURE/MAYBE:
    - Add appveyor.yml

WHEN RELEASING FIRST TIME
    1.: create and edit properly package.json (version, etc)
    2.: run "grunt build"
    3.: commit and add new version tag (GitHub tag) (do NOT push immediately)
    4.: push all to GitHub
    5.: run "npm publish"
    6.: run "bower register packageName git://github.com/username/projectName.git"